      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Cypriot-style lean beef mince kebabs</strong> with the <strong>sumac salad</strong> and <strong>chilli pittas</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining ground sumac</strong> and garnish with the <strong>lemon wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
